      "title": "Sri Lanka Party leader arrested for harboring murder suspects",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Saman Perera, the leader of 'Ape Jana Bala Pakshaya' or Our Power of People Party was arrested by Police in Kosgoda on Wednesday (24).",
        "The suspect was arrested on the charge of harboring suspects wanted for a murder that took place in Tangalle recently.",
        "IMF delegation in Sri Lanka for talks on economic and financial reforms"
